Susan Collins has gun deaths on her hands. She wants you to believe she’s a “leader” on gun reform, but in reality, Susan falls right in line with her party when it comes to taking action. That’s because she won’t break with Mitch McConnell when it matters most and doesn’t want to provoke the NRA (who bankrolls her campaign).

Susan Collins is all talk. Chip in to replace her with someone who will lead on gun reform - not offer condolences.
funding_entity: Be a Hero PAC. Not authorized by any candidate or candidate’s committee.

ad_creative_body:
Susan Collins claims she wants to “get something done that makes a difference” on gun reform, but every time she has the power to do so, she chooses to vote with Mitch McConnell and the NRA. Meanwhile, communities across America are being ripped apart by gun violence, like the tragedies that just occurred in El Paso and Dayton.

Replacing Susan in 2020 will take a lot of resources, but there’s no limit on what our grassroots movement can achieve. Chip in to our people-powered campaign to hold Susan Collins accountable for her lack of action.
funding_entity: Be a Hero PAC. Not authorized by any candidate or candidate’s committee.

ad_creative_body:
Susan Collins is no “maverick” or independent voice in the Senate and her voting record proves it. In fact, she’s voting along party lines now more than ever before. When you’re loyal to Donald Trump and Mitch McConnell and taking thousands of dollars from the NRA, it’s impossible to take any real action to prevent gun violence.

Hundreds of mass shootings are happening under her watch, so we’re building a people-powered movement to unseat her. Chip in now - your donation goes directly towards our work to kick out Collins in 2020.
funding_entity: Be a Hero PAC. Not authorized by any candidate or candidate’s committee.

ad_creative_body:
As a Senator, Susan Collins should want to stop the gun violence that rips communities like El Paso and Dayton apart. But each time she has the power to do something about it, she refuses to break with Mitch McConnell and the NRA. In her 22 years in the Senate, she’s voted against banning assault weapons, against fixing holes in the background check system, and voted with the NRA to allow unchecked concealed weapons everywhere in the country.

That’s not the kind of leadership we need in the Senate. If enough of us step up, we can build a grassroots campaign that’s strong enough to unseat her and flip the Senate in 2020. Chip in to help us hold Susan accountable.
funding_entity: Be a Hero PAC. Not authorized by any candidate or candidate’s committee.

ad_creative_body:
As a Senator, Susan Collins has real power to do something about the gun violence tearing apart communities across the country. But in her 22 years in the Senate, on every critical vote, she has sided with the NRA against gun safety including: banning assault weapons, ending the manufacture of 20 and 30-round ammunition magazines, fixing the holes in the background check system, and stopping the transfer of guns to suspected terrorists, just to name a few.

We need a Senator who backs up their words with action - not bows down to the NRA. Chip in $20.20 to power our work to replace Susan in 2020.
funding_entity: Be a Hero PAC. Not authorized by any candidate or candidate’s committee.

ad_creative_body:
To stop the extreme right-wing turn in U.S. policy, we must do more than just defeat Donald Trump. We have to take back the U.S. Senate. Susan Collins is a big part of the problem. For example, despite the wave of mass shootings, she consistently sides with the NRA and against gun safety -- as she has done for the past 20 years.

Each dollar we raise helps us recruit one more volunteer, make one more phone call, knock on one more door, and earn one more vote against Susan Collins. Donate $20.20 to help us defeat Collins and end Trumpism.
funding_entity: Be a Hero PAC. Not authorized by any candidate or candidate’s committee.
